    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that defines the term 'mint.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, and its condition reflects a level of care rarely seen. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like clarity with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. All glass is original and crystal clear, and the factory alloy wheels are free of any curb rash or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats remain firm and supple with zero wear on the bolsters, and the original carpets have been protected by factory mats since new. Every switch, button, and digital display functions with tactile precision, and the interior still retains its distinct showroom aroma. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has a comprehensive, documented service history from authorized dealers, ensuring the engine and transmission operate with seamless smoothness. There are no fluid leaks, no unusual noises, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This sale includes all original keys, the owner\u2019s manual portfolio, and a complete binder of maintenance receipts. For the buyer who demands perfection and a turn-key experience, this vehicle stands as the definitive example.",
